  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e01\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003eAITA for refusing to “give up” my dog’s name so my sister can use it for her baby?\u003c/h2\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10515781120/h1EB1FF08/yell-aurora-together-at-dragon-part-name-is-daily-reminder-mom-and-honestly-got-through-her-passing\" id=\"_r_a_10515781120\" width=\"576\" height=\"527\" alt=\"I (29 F) have a 3-year-old golden retriever named Aurora. I picked the name because when my late mom read us bedtime stories, Sleeping Beauty was her favorite and we\u0026#39;d always yell \u0026#34;AURORA!\u0026#34; together at the dragon part. The name is a daily reminder of mom and honestly got me through her passing.\" title=\"AITA for refusing to “give up” my dog’s name so my sister can use it for her baby?\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e02\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10516161536/hA9318C50\" id=\"_r_a_10516161536\" width=\"800\" height=\"420\" alt=\"Cheezburger Image 10516161536\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n            \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003csub\u003eThe image does not depict the actual subjects of the story. Subjects are models. \u003c/sub\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e03\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10515781632/h80A7072C/name-aurora-smiled-and-said-great-choiceshell-share-with-worlds-goofiest-dog-s-everything-blew-up\" id=\"_r_a_10515781632\" width=\"581\" height=\"482\" alt=\"My sister \u0026#34;Emily\u0026#34; (31 F) is 28 weeks pregnant with her first child. Two weeks ago at a family BBQ she announced she\u0026#39;d chosen the perfect name: Aurora. I smiled and said \u0026#34;Great choice—she\u0026#39;ll share with the world\u0026#39;s goofiest dog.” That\u0026#39;s when everything blew up.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e04\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10515781376/h7D29B4E2\" id=\"_r_a_10515781376\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" alt=\"Cheezburger Image 10515781376\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n            \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003csub\u003eThe image does not depict the actual subjects of the story. Subjects are models.\u003c/sub\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e05\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10515781888/hF2018EA0/so-should-rename-my-dog-or-at-least-stop-using-name-publicly-aurora-has-an-insta-with-8-k-followers\" id=\"_r_a_10515781888\" width=\"586\" height=\"461\" alt=\"Emily pulled me aside and said: 1. It\u0026#39;s tacky for cousins/nieces to share a name with a pet. 2. I\u0026#39;ve \u0026#34;had my fun,\u0026#34; so I should rename my dog or at least stop using the name publicly (Aurora has an Insta with ~8 k followers).\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e06\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10515782144/h7C83F539/stealing-her-moment-and-dishonoring-our-mom-because-real-daughters-name-babies-after-moms-not-dogs\" id=\"_r_a_10515782144\" width=\"566\" height=\"318\" alt=\"3. If I keep the name, I\u0026#39;m \u0026#34;stealing her moment\u0026#34; and dishonoring our mom because \u0026#34;real daughters name babies after moms, not dogs.\u0026#34;\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e07\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10515782400/hF8B8AA87/aurora-my-dogs-official-middle-name-on-insta-so-her-baby-would-still-be-only-human-aurora-family\" id=\"_r_a_10515782400\" width=\"577\" height=\"533\" alt=\"I told her Aurora\u0026#39;s name is staying. It\u0026#39;s on vet records, training certificates, microchip forms— changing it feels wrong and pointless. I suggested plenty of alternatives (Aria, Aurelia, Rory) and offered to make Aurora my dog\u0026#39;s official middle name on Insta so her baby would still be the only human Aurora in the family.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e08\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10515782656/hA8AAC167/niece-dad-tried-mediating-he-thinks-should-compromise-because-babies-matter-more-than-dogs-our\" id=\"_r_a_10515782656\" width=\"582\" height=\"367\" alt=\"Emily refused, started crying, and called me \u0026#34;a selfish child-free moron who cares more about a dog than her future niece.\u0026#34; Dad tried mediating; he thinks I should compromise \u0026#34;because babies matter more than dogs.\u0026#34; Our\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e09\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10515782912/h70DDE3E3/group-chat-has-been-on-fire-days-and-getting-texts-like-enjoy-ruining-my-first-mothers-day\" id=\"_r_a_10515782912\" width=\"582\" height=\"308\" alt=\"matter more than dogs.\u0026#34; Our brother says Emily is being ridiculous. Group chat has been on fire for days and I\u0026#39;m getting texts like \u0026#34;Enjoy ruining my first Mother\u0026#39;s Day\u0026#34; (??).\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e10\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10515783168/h60DB5762/by-posting-poll-on-facebook-should-my-sister-rename-her-dog-so-my-baby-can-have-name-tagging\" id=\"_r_a_10515783168\" width=\"568\" height=\"261\" alt=\"Yesterday Emily nuked the situation by posting a poll on Facebook: \u0026#34;Should my sister rename her dog so my baby can have the name?\u0026#34;-tagging me.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e11\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10516174080/h2007DF53\" id=\"_r_a_10516174080\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" alt=\"Cheezburger Image 10516174080\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e12\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10515783424/h93E5B98F/is-voting-and-people-barely-know-are-dm-ing-opinions-muted-everything-and-took-aurora-on-long-hike\" id=\"_r_a_10515783424\" width=\"566\" height=\"253\" alt=\"Now half the extended family is voting, and people I barely know are DM-ing me opinions. I muted everything and took Aurora on a long hike.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e13\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10515783680/h56F03EA7/apologize-keep-peace-feel-backed-into-corner-but-also-wonder-if-being-petty-over-just-dog-name-aita\" id=\"_r_a_10515783680\" width=\"567\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Family dinner is this Sunday and Dad says I\u0026#39;m expected to apologize to \u0026#34;keep the peace.\u0026#34; I feel backed into a corner but also wonder if I\u0026#39;m being petty over “just a dog name.\u0026#34; AITA?\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eOf course, like any sane person, Reddit sided with the pup over the human in this story. After all, the dog claimed the name first. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e14\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10515785728/hC434A76A/scsoutherngal-tell-sister-would-be-overjoyed-her-name-her-child-after-dog-nta\" id=\"_r_a_10515785728\" width=\"737\" height=\"197\" alt=\"scsoutherngal Tell your sister that you would be overjoyed for her to name her child after your dog. NTA\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e15\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10515784448/hDC53CD57/as-our-brothers-dog-and-total-non-issue-s-just-name-sister-needs-get-some-real-problems-worry-about\" id=\"_r_a_10515784448\" width=\"742\" height=\"251\" alt=\"CommunicationEasy142 My sister called her daughter the same name as our brother\u0026#39;s dog and it was a total non-issue. It\u0026#39;s just a name. Your sister needs to get some real problems to worry about.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e16\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10515786240/hAD62163B/calvin-not-hobbes-so-sister-is-narcissist\" id=\"_r_a_10515786240\" width=\"402\" height=\"122\" alt=\"calvin-not-Hobbes so...your sister is a narcissist.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e17\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10515784704/h8CBB981D/she-knew-she-made-her-voice-s-fine-if-they-both-have-same-name-but-no-mistake-she-made-choice-not\" id=\"_r_a_10515784704\" width=\"753\" height=\"536\" alt=\"anditurnedaround Just to make sure I understand..,, you named your dog first right? Why would she name her child after your known dog name and then expect you to change your dogs name. That\u0026#39;s ridiculous. She knew. She made her voice. It\u0026#39;s fine if they both have the same name but no mistake she made that choice, not you.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e18\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10515784192/hF49EE6D5/dog-but-as-she-grows-up-she-will-probably-think-s-cool-having-same-name-as-dog-would-find-non-issue\" id=\"_r_a_10515784192\" width=\"768\" height=\"290\" alt=\"ChessingtonSurrey NTA. Realistically, your niece will outlive your dog. But as she grows up she will probably think it\u0026#39;s cool having the same name as your dog... I would find it a non issue.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e19\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10515783936/h1DC8C6FD/this-family-lol-not-mention-facebook-poll-yall-need-get-off-social-media-and-touch-some-grass-lol\" id=\"_r_a_10515783936\" width=\"777\" height=\"367\" alt=\"Seaworthypear The fact that your dog has 8k followers tells me everything I need to know about this family lol Not to mention the Facebook poll Y\u0026#39;all need to get off social media and touch some grass lol\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAnd how confusing it would be for the dog\u0026#39;s loyal 8k Instagram followers if all of a sudden their beloved Aurora had a new name! \u003c/p\u003e\n\n    \u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n            \u003cp\u003eStay up to date by following us on \u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FailBlog\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eFacebook\u003c/a\u003e!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n                \u003ch2\u003eTags\u003c/h2\u003e\n        \n\n            \n\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\n        \n        \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eScroll Down For The Next Article\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n                \n\n 